Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning little friends,\Nyour singing is oh so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is a very\Nbeautiful day today,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly something\Nworth singing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ There's music in the treetops\Nand there's music in the vale. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and all around me{\i0}\N{\i1}music fills the sky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ There's music by the river {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and there's music{\i0}\N{\i1}in the grass ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And the music makes your{\i0}\N{\i1}heart soar in reply ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Aahhhh! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Aaaaahhh! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Ah ha ha! Ah ha ha! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Aaaaah! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Ah ha ha! Ah ha ha! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:01:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much.\NYou're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}WOW!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You um, you didn't\Nhear me, um ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Singing in the most\Nbeautiful voice ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I've never heard you\Nsing a solo like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a little\Nslice of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With ice cream on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, I cannot believe\Nyour spectacular voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't part of the\NPony Tones Quartet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...well...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since you're\Nhaving us perform
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for your Ponyville Pet Center\NFundraiser tomorrow night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This simply must be rectified!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You must share that\Nstunning voice at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It will be so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be there on stage,\Nbasking in the hooflights,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the center of attention,\Na shining star...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With everypony staring{\i0}\N{\i1}at you, judging you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,jealously noting how they\Ncould be WAY better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wasn't it them?\NWhy wasn't it them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, when you choke,{\i0}\N{\i1}they'll turn on you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming a seething angry mob
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be horribly\Nhumiliated,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,never able to show your\Nface in Ponyville again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Don't\Nbe ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You will join the group making\Nthe Pony Tones Quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the Pony Tones Quintet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the Pony Tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of their biggest fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do not want to\Nperform with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you see, I...I\Nhave...um...I-I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have...stage fright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it contagious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage fright isn't\Na disease, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means that Fluttershy\Nis scared to perform
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very thankful\Nthe Pony Tones
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,are singing at the Pet\NCenter Fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm really looking{\i0}\N{\i1}forward to the performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll be watching\Nsafely from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's a terrible\Nwaste of an exquisite talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I understand that\Nyou're not comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:03:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Angel's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of work to\Ndo before tomorrow's event!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Pony Tones, let's\Nrun through that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Everypony's saying you should\N{\i1}learn to express your voice. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But if talk doesn't seem{\i0}\N{\i1}like it's the answer ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ luckily you have a choice. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ When you find you've got the{\i0}\N{\i1}music, got the music in you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Find you've got the music{\i0}\N{\i1}got the music in you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Spike, but\Nthis is an ensemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Enh, the rest of you\Nwere pretty good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought you were all\Namazing, Pony Tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Pony Tones, I want you\Nall to rest your voices
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for the remainder of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a final run-through\Ntomorrow before the big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity, the Pony Tones\Nare really going to make
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ponyville Pet Center\NFundraiser so special!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for\Nhelping me help the animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes. It is wonderful\Nwhen a plan comes together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,without any sort of\Ndrama, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning,\NPony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we're the Pony\NTones minus one tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac is\Ninconveniently late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I not told you\Nabout punctuality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I don't want\Nto hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac! Can you please\Nstart the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nnope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever did you\Ndo to cause this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And welcome to the 12th Annual\NPonyville Turkey Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will take the\Ntitle this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be somepony new?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will the Turkey Call\Nchampion of six years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}defend his title to make{\i0}\N{\i1}it lucky number seven?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out if\Nya stop yer gabbin'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and git on with\Nthe gobblin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac, yer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A Turkey Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your voice\Ndoing a...Turkey Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost his voice and the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can't\Nperform tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise the fundraiser\Nwill be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we cannot perform\Ntonight with only three voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take rearranging\Nall the music
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and we just don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Fluttershy,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I have no remedy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for this situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A remedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahhhh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cure this\Npony that is hoarse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will take\Na longer course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can mix a brew that\Nwill work just right,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but it cannot heal\Nhim by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we ever going\Nto find a deep voice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to replace Big Mac's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Zecora,\Nbut this is no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a bass voice for\Nthe harmonies to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Without it, the\Nperformance will be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my\Nstrange elation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was not laughing\Nat your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when you pony folk\Nstumbled into Poison Joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Fluttershy had{\i0}\N{\i1}an unusual change,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}deepening her vocal range.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to\Ntalk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice became really\Nlow, making it sound like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Flutterguy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With these leaves,\NI can mix a brew
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,creating the same\Neffect on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora, that's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything for the animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you'd even\Nappear on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, except that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't bring\Nmyself to sing on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you sang NOT\Nin front of everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Big Mac was on\Nstage moving his lips
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're behind the\Ncurtain singing his part?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be just like\Nsinging in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nopony would know it was you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even still. I just don't think\NI could sing in front of--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You must! For the animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK, then...mix it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do it just\Nlike we practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening,\Ncitizens of Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you all\Nfor coming out tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and generously supporting\Nthe Ponyville Pet Center!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to your kindness, pets{\i0}\N{\i1}are finding loving homes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we are sure to meet{\i0}\N{\i1}our fundraising goal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prob'ly hidin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how much that\Npony hates the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, with no further ado, please\Nwelcome...The Pony Tones!
