Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony Tones! Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was truly amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you sounded better\Nthan ever, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you were on the\Nwrong side of the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally missed the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a true professional,\NFluttershy was back stage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,making sure everything\Nran smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fantastic, Pony Tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My new puppy and I thought it\Nwas super duper crazy good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were wondering if you\Nwould consider performing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,at my daughter\NZippoorwhill's Cuteciñera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you? Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When is it? Next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gracious, I'm\Nterribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just much\Ntoo last-minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't disappoint\Nthat sweet little filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nyou're up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ When you find{\i0}\N{\i1}you've got the music, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}got the music in you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Find you've got the music,{\i0}\N{\i1}got the music in you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Got the music, got{\i0}\N{\i1}the music in you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We got the Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would be even more\Namazing if you could perform
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at my ribbon-cutting\Nceremony tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mayor, we would\Nlove to but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you excuse us\Nfor a second, Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't\Nworry, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nperform again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But we wouldn't\Nwant to disappoint the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then Mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the Pony Tones will happily perform\Nat your ceremony!
