Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Sky is clear and{\i0}\N{\i1}you're feeling so fine. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Everything's going{\i0}\N{\i1}to be a-ok. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want to\Ndisappoint the spa patrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ If you listen carefully {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ on every corner there's{\i0}\N{\i1}a rhythm playing. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Then it happens suddenly{\i0}\N{\i1}the music takes you over ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't want to disappoint\Nthe school ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and you find you{\i0}\N{\i1}got the music. ♪{\i0}
