Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Find it, oh yeah ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Got the music in you now ♪{\i0}
