Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! We\Nmust talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac's voice\Nis all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can bathe in the\NPoison Joke antidote
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and sound like your\Nlovely self again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...I didn't know\Nthat last performance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,was my last  performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be OK if Fluttershy\Nsang for you one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey-o, you can find it, find{\i0}\N{\i1}it in your heart yeah yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Find the music yeah yeah, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ it's in you right now,{\i0}\N{\i1}oh yeah, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ you can find the music,{\i0}\N{\i1}I love the music yeah! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some 'splainin' to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Turkey call?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Trash yer voice?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora remedy?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quick enough?\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Needed a deep voice?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison Joke?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Flutterguy?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Better now?\NEeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that shy filly was living\Nher dream in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because she couldn't\Nbring herself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to come into the\Nspotlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for corn's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was totally{\i0}\N{\i1}unbelievable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the curtain came\Nup, and there you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,singing in front of everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, I don't think\Nany pony was jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,cause there certainly\Nwasn't an angry mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must have been horrible\Nstanding there on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All eyes glued directly on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you were living your\Nown personal worst nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What Pinkie meant to say was\Nthat you were really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Didn't I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE GREAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally blew\Nmy mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, no offence, you\Nkind of sounded like a dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A great sounding dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I'm never going to\Nsing in front of anypony
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we please\Nstop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand\Nwhy, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, you're the one{\i0}\N{\i1}that wanted the Pony Tones{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to sing for every silly\Nthing that was requested of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you knew I\Nreally wanted to perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And for all her babbling, Pinkie\NPie was right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When that curtain fell, and\Neverypony saw you singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you lived your worst nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what was so bad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The thunderous\Napplause?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The praise for your\Nfantastic singin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The SCREAMING FANS?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ There's music in the treetops\Nand there's music in the vale ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and all around the{\i0}\N{\i1}music fills the sky. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ There's music by the river and\N{\i1}there's music in the grass. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And the music makes your{\i0}\N{\i1}heart soar into flight. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you find you've{\i0}\N{\i1}got the music,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ You've got to look{\i0}\N{\i1}inside and find. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Find you've got the music {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ The music deep inside you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Find you've got the music. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Cause when you look{\i0}\N{\i1}inside you'll see it. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ You're going to find,{\i0}\N{\i1}you're going to find. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Got the music, got{\i0}\N{\i1}the music...in you! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it,\NFluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That\Nwasn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't look completely\Npetrified by the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're all staring\Nat you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fantastic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the Pony Tones\Nhave been booked for the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Family's Zap Apple\NJam Extraordinaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I couldn't\Ndo that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?\NHow come?\NSeriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get there someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, baby\Nsteps, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby steps.
